国际日期</a>。</p><p>门票于本周六（8 月 31 日）上午 9 点（英国夏令时）开始公开发售 – <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Doasis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里</a>（英国）和<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.ie%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Doasis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>（爱尔兰）购买门票。粉丝们还可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-share-details-of-reunion-tour-pre-sale-ballot-sign-up-here-3787970">报名参加投票，以便在英国夏令时间今天 (28) 晚上 7 点之前周五 (30) 进行预售</a>。</p><p>在其他地方，Ticketmaster 还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-2025-ticketmaster-share-strict-rules-for-buying-tickets-3787960">向那些希望获得即将到来的团圆巡演门票的人分享了严格的规则</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">周五（8 月 30 日），乐队发布了 1994 年开创性首张专辑《Definitely Maybe》的 30 周年纪念再版，</a>此前，备受期待的巡演消息传出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-will-reportedly-make-more-than-400million-3787259">据报道预计将赚得 4 亿英镑</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3775018" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3775018" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3775018" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270.jpg" alt="绿洲乐队的利亚姆·加拉格尔和诺埃尔·加拉格尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" />